criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  going through thoracoscopic lung surgery including lobectomy, segmentectomy, single or
             multiple wedge resection, and two of the above procedures combined;

          -  able to complete the pain scoring face-to-face;

          -  no cognitive dysfunction or history of anesthetic drug allergy;

          -  ASA grade I-II

        Exclusion Criteria:

        -psychological disorders
